               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir “The Five Pillars of Mystery” (fols. 1v-45r),
                     incomplete
 I-1) Mǝśṭira ṭǝmqat “Mystery of Baptism” (fols. 1v-20r)
                     I-2) Mǝśṭira qʷǝrbān “Mystery of the Eucharist” (fols. 20r-32r)
 I-3)
                     Mǝśṭira tǝnśāʾe mutān “Mystery of the Resurrection of the
                     Dead”(32r-45r)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title type="incomplete">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir</title>
                     <note>only three out of five mysteries</note>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <title>Mǝśṭira ṭǝmqat</title>                    
                        
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <title>Mǝśṭira qʷǝrbān</title>                    
                        
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <title>Mǝśṭira tǝnśāʾe</title>                    
                        
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
